item.title: The Mount Sinai Brain Bank (MSBB) study info
item.description: The Mount Sinai Brain Bank (MSBB) study info # This cohort study generated large-scale matched multi-Omics data in AD and control brains for exploring novel molecular underpinnings of AD. PI : Prof. Bin Zhang Institution : Icahn School of Medicine at Mount Sinai Grant number : U01AG046170, RF1AG057440, RF1AG054014, R01AG057907 Contact person : Minghui Wang ( minghui.wang@mssm.edu) Publication : PMID: 30204156, 33238137 Acknowledgement : This work was supported by the grants from the NIH/National Institute on Aging (NIA).
